      <title>交易员预计中国债券收益率将跌至 1.5%，因市场普遍看好股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/traders-see-china-yield-fall-to-1-5-on-everything-rally-hope</link>
